title: #125 - Oliver Tree
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we're joined in studio by musician, artist, social media star, razor scooter expert and living meme: Oliver Tree! Together we discuss growing up in Santa Cruz, going to Ukraine to shoot a music video, pranking the president of Atlantic Records, his bowl cut, and a whole lot more!
itunes:author: Ethan Klein
